org.lwjgl.ovr

Class OVRTimewarpProjectionDesc

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lwjgl.ovr.OVRTimewarpProjectionDesc
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pointer

    public final class OVRTimewarpProjectionDesc
extends java.lang.Object
implements Pointer
    Projection information for OVRLayerEyeFovDepth.

    Use the utility function OVRUtil.ovrTimewarpProjectionDesc_FromProjection(java.nio.ByteBuffer, int, java.nio.ByteBuffer) to generate this structure from the application's projection matrix.
